      <h2>Is this a new type of syllabus?</h2>
      <p>Yes. The traditional syllabus is out of alignment with today's hybrid and online learning environments.</p> 
      <p>SALSAs are designed to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>deliver information in a learner-centric format</li>
        <li>incorporate measurable learning outcomes/objectives</li>
        <li>meet requirements for web accessibility</li>
        <li>provide responsive layouts for mobile devices</li>
      </ul>
    </div><!-- /.col-sm-6 -->
